Module com.kohlschutter.junixsocket.nativecommon

Package org.newsclub.lib.junixsocket.common

package org.newsclub.lib.junixsocket.common
Helper package to identify the Maven artifact with JNI libraries for common architectures. The set of common architectures is configured through Maven profiles and should at least contain versions for Intel 64-bit macOS and Linux.
